
Create 2 Tables: Worker , Bonus. (Format as provided below).
CREATE TABLE WORKER( 
	WORKER_ID INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	FIRST_NAME CHAR(25),
	LAST_NAME CHAR(25),
	SALARY INT(15),
	JOINING_DATE DATETIME,
	DEPARTMENT CHAR(25)); 
  
CREATE TABLE Bonus( 
	WORKER_REF_ID INT,
	BONUS_AMOUNT INT(10),
	BONUS_DATE DATETIME);
	
  Insert Values in the tables as described, and display all the values of both tables separately.  (Values provided below.)
  
